==Italian==

===Noun phrase===
'''[[pasta]] con le [[sarde]]'''

# a [[Sicilian]] [[dish]] of pasta served with a [[sauce]] containing [[sardine]]s, [[anchovies]], [[fennel]], [[raisin]]s, [[pine nut]]s and [[saffron]]

===Usage notes===
*Supposedly "pasta con le sarde a mare" (pasta with the sardines at sea) is the same dish without the sardines or any expensive ingredient